<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Fragment from the lower part of a <rs type="objectType">stele</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.29</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.295</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.21</measure>). Back, and perhaps lower edge, survive.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on one face, which is very worn and abraded.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Very irregular; cursive <term lang="grc-Latn">alpha</term>; <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.01-0.02</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>Possibly <date cert="low" exact="none" notBefore="0250" notAfter="0400">after A.D. 250</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
